des:
Use Alexa to control your Crorzar home smart devices! After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our “Crorzar Home” app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in our “Crorzar Home” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4) Search “Crorzar Home” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5) Enable “Crorzar Home” skill, and you'll be navigated to “Crorzar Home” login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on the fan in the bathroom
Alexa, turn on the bedroom light
Alexa, turn off the bedroom light
Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%
Alexa, set bedroom light to green
Alexa, turn on master bedroom TV
Alexa, show the back yard Crorzar Cameras
